---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="LUFEP | Inicio"
	activeNav="home"
	description="Servicios de diseño y desarrollo web premium para profesionales que buscan sitios web altamente convertidores, rápidos y confiables."
>
	<main>
		<section class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl gap-10 px-6 py-14 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
			<div class="space-y-5">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1E3A8A]">Expert Web Solutions</p>
				<h1 class="max-w-lg text-[42px] font-semibold leading-[1.15] text-[#1C1917]">
					Websites that build trust for your business
				</h1>
				<p class="max-w-md text-base leading-7 text-[#78716C]">
					We craft precision-engineered digital experiences for professionals who value reliability,
					speed, and quiet authority.
				</p>
				<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
					<a href="/portafolio" class="rounded-sm bg-[#1E3A8A] px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white">See Portfolio</a>
					<a href="/services" class="rounded-sm border border-[#E7E5E4] bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Our Process</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="relative max-w-[520px]">
				<img
					src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1498050108023-c5249f4df085?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
					alt="Escritorio profesional"
					class="h-[350px] w-full rounded-md object-cover"
				/>
				<div class="absolute -bottom-6 left-6 rounded-sm bg-white px-5 py-3 shadow-sm">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-[#1E3A8A]">99.9%</p>
					<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[#78716C]">Uptime Guaranteed</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="border-y border-[#E7E5E4] bg-[#F6F2EB]">
			<div class="mx-auto grid w-full max-w-6xl grid-cols-2 gap-6 px-6 py-7 text-center text-sm text-[#78716C] md:grid-cols-6">
				<span class="md:col-span-1">Trusted by industry leaders in</span>
				<span>Legal</span>
				<span>Finance</span>
				<span>Hospitality</span>
				<span>Healthcare</span>
				<span>Real Estate</span>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-6 py-16">
			<p class="text-center text-sm text-[#78716C]">Designed for Professionals</p>
			<h2 class="mt-3 text-center text-3xl font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Quiet authority, modern execution.</h2>
			<p class="mx-auto mt-3 max-w-2xl text-center text-sm leading-6 text-[#78716C]">
				We understand the unique needs of service-oriented businesses where credibility is your most
				valuable asset.
			</p>

			<div class="mt-10 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-6">
				<article class="rounded-md border border-[#E7E5E4] bg-white p-6 md:col-span-4">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Unmatched Speed</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 max-w-lg text-base leading-7 text-[#78716C]">
						Our lightweight architectures ensure your site loads instantly, keeping high-intent
						clients engaged from the first second.
					</p>
					<img
						src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
						alt="Analitica de crecimiento"
						class="mt-6 h-44 w-full rounded-sm object-cover"
					/>
				</article>
				<article class="rounded-md border border-[#E7E5E4] bg-white p-6 md:col-span-2">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Quiet Authority</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-[#78716C]">
						We avoid flashy trends. Instead, we use structured layouts and premium typography.
					</p>
					<ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-[#78716C]">
						<li>• Clean architectural layouts</li>
						<li>• Sober professional palettes</li>
						<li>• Accessibility-first design</li>
					</ul>
				</article>
				<article class="rounded-md border border-[#E7E5E4] bg-white p-6 md:col-span-2">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Simplicity First</h3>
					<p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-[#78716C]">
						Manage your content without a degree in engineering. Our custom backend is built for
						humans, not robots.
					</p>
				</article>
				<article class="grid rounded-md border border-[#E7E5E4] bg-white p-6 md:col-span-4 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center md:gap-5">
					<img
						src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80"
						alt="Equipo profesional"
						class="h-36 w-full rounded-sm object-cover"
					/>
					<div class="mt-4 md:mt-0">
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1C1917]">Industry-Specific SEO</h3>
						<p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-[#78716C]">
							We build search authority for local legal, accounting, and hospitality sectors.
						</p>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="bg-[#1C1917]">
			<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-6xl px-6 py-16 text-center text-white">
				<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold">Ready to elevate your digital presence?</h2>
				<p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-white/80">
					Start a project with us today and receive a detailed consultation on how we can transform
					your business website into a trust-building engine.
				</p>
				<a href="/contact" class="mt-8 inline-block rounded-sm bg-[#E07856] px-9 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white">
					Start Your Project Today
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
